      "raw_text": "Suffrage will be preached from\ntwo pulpits in the city Sunday\nnight. Ex-Governor John P. st.\nJohn of Kansas will speak on\nEqual Suffrage\" at the First\nUnited Brethren church, corner Of\nBaldwin and Lidgerwood. At the\nNorwegian Danish Methodist\nchurch. S217 Stevenson, the pastor.\nRev. G.. August Petersen, Will\nspeak in Norwegian. and Mrs. M.\nJ. Reynolds, the suffrage speaker\nfrom Colorado, will speak in Eng\nfish. Miss Fay Morvillius will sing\nat this meeting."
